> __**Mechanics**__
.tag:mechanics
He will only attack with Necromancy and only has 2 mechanics that differ from autos.
⬥ **Smash**
    • When he does this he will draw back his sword and hit your current location. This will disable your protection prayers.
⬥ **Conjure**
    • Roughly every 48 seconds he will summon 2 armoured phantoms and become completely immune to damage until they are dead.

.
> __**Action Bars**__
.tag:rots
There are 2 different revolution bars for high level and mid level.
Both of which require <:igneouskalmor:1139200072438005851> / <:igneouskalzuk:902209626479685734>.

**High Level Action Bar (40-60kph)**
